  MIT License — see packages/daemon/LICENSE

- packages/server (@loopany/server, the Loopany platform server):
  GNU Affero General Public License v3.0 only (AGPL-3.0-only) —
  see packages/server/LICENSE

  Exception: the contents of packages/server/src/skill/ that are bundled into
  the daemon npm package by packages/daemon/scripts/sync-skill.mjs (SKILL.md and
  the references/ files) are licensed under the MIT License, so the published
  daemon package is MIT in its entirety.

Everything else in this repository (root configuration, scripts, docs) is
licensed under AGPL-3.0-only unless a file or directory states otherwise.

